But this would indicate in their language and in ours, I think we could say that his rule is strong and just.

211
00:18:35.000 --> 00:18:43.000
It is not one that yields, it's not soft, it's not flimsy, it's firm.

212
00:18:43.000 --> 00:18:54.000
Now, recognizing the nature of the story we're in and the character of the author and what his plan might be,

213
00:18:54.000 --> 00:19:04.000
how can we best participate? Work, play, laugh, cry, love, fall, get back up in this story.

214
00:19:04.000 --> 00:19:08.000
I'm glad you asked. I'm glad you're on that question too.

215
00:19:08.000 --> 00:19:21.000
In verse 10 it says, now therefore, be wise, O Kings, be warned, O rulers of the earth.

216
00:19:21.000 --> 00:19:26.000
Now, again this is one that I would kind of gloss over. I'm not a ruler of the earth.

217
00:19:26.000 --> 00:19:34.000
I go to my job, I try to maintain my household imperfectly as my wife can attest.

218
00:19:35.000 --> 00:19:38.000
